Dialogs.Dialog: Good morning！ We meet again today！
Right when I wanted to talk with you. Hehe.
Ah, okay. It's all right. Let's talk.
I'll try to stay awake so I can talk with you▼
Even though it's already late, will you talk with me？
I'm feeling sleepy. But if you want to talk with me, it's all right.
Good morning. Let's do our best today.
You just woke up？ It's already noon.
Oh my. You just woke up at this hour？
It's already late. Did you change your daily rhythm？
Did you wake up because you can't stay asleep？
Good morning. You're an early riser. Do you have anything going on today？
Eh？ You're going to sleep now？
Sleeping at this hour... You didn't sleep well last night, did you？
Good night. Have a nice dream, okay？
Good night. Sleeping late, aren't you？
Finally going to bed？ Will you be able to wake up on time？
Do you have anything to ask me？
Is there anything strange on my face？
...What？ If you look at me like that, I'll get embarrassed, you know？
Aren't you excited for our next date？
Yes. Together we'll make it into a lovely date.
Oh, come on. It's a date I've been waiting for.
Our recent date was very exciting, wasn't it？
You think so, too？ We'll make the next one as unforgettable as that one, okay？
Hmm, somehow I feel like I'm such a fool.
Thank you very much for the gift. I'm very glad.
I'm happy to have someone who I can give presents to and receive presents from.
Eh？ What？ A token of gratitude for the present...？
Hey, who are you thinking about right now？
Hmm, that person must be so cute, huh？
Hmm, that person must be so lovely, huh？
Let's stop it already. You're teasing me.
What's wrong？ Didn't you hear what I said？
It'll be Valentine's Day soon. Aren't you expecting it？ Teehee.
Hmm... You won't be discouraging me.
It'll be Christmas soon, right？ Will you spend it with your girlfriend？
Teehee▼ I wonder why Christmas won't come sooner.
Whatever. Don't you know that I've been expecting it？
It'll be our anniversary soon. Do you remember？
Hehe, you remember it after all. I'm so happy.
It's your birthday soon. Are you looking forward to it？
Yes！ Let's celebrate it together, okay？
Soon, it'll be my birthday. Do you remember？
Well, I'm kind of expecting something from you, you know？
The year's almost over. Has it been a wonderful year？
I think so too. It's because you're by my side.
Is that so？ Hmm... well, it's nothing.
The new semester is starting soon. Are you excited？
Hehe, we can be together at school, right？
Hehe. Is that so？ You haven't finished your homework, have you？
Tests are coming up. Have you already studied？
No... it's bad. You must study, okay？
Soon it'll be spring. Do you like spring？
Yeah, I want to go flower viewing.
Is that so？ I wonder if you're allergic to pollen.
Soon it'll be summer. Do you like summer？
Yeah. Let's make a lot of memories at the beach and at festivals, okay？
Is that so？ Do you dislike the heat？
Soon it'll be fall. Do you like fall？
It's the time to appreciate the arts, literature... And sweet potatoes. Teehee♪
It's not a season for everyone, I guess. But, Manaka will always be with you, all right？
Soon it'll be winter. Do you like winter？
There will be Christmas, and then Valentine's Day. Somehow, it feels like a season for lovers, right？
It's not like that, you know？
Hey, can you tell me your favorite color？
Is that so？ Okay, I'll remember it.
You like such a weird color, eh？
Hey, hey. Can you tell me your favorite food？
Teehee, me too. It's really delicious, isn't it？
Is that... so？ I don't quite like it.
Is that so？ I don't think I've ever eaten that.
Hey, what kind of outfit would you like me to wear？
Okay, I'll remember that. However, don't expect too much, okay？
No！ Never！ You must be thinking of something perverted...
Is that so？ I'll remember this for later, then.
Hey, what kind of movies do you like？
Ah, me too. Teehee. We're the same, right▼？
Hmm... I don't quite like those.
Hmm... I don't think I've seen those.
What kind of event would you like to see at the event hall？
Yes, Sounds great！ Let's go together next time, okay？
Where would you like to go for a date？
Yeah, me too. Let's go together.
Hmm... if you like it, then it's okay.
Is that so？ If it's the place you like, then it's okay, I guess.
Hey, if I were an animal, what would I be？
Teehee, I'm glad. I really like rabbit▼
Huh...？ I didn't think you'd say that.
Well, do you have a favorite store？
Ah, I like it too！ Shall we go there now？ Teehee♪
Is that so？ I don't know much about it. Take me there next time, okay？
Hey, hey... Do you love me？
Okay. Teehee, I just wanted to hear it every once in a while.
That's embarrassing... I also love you so much▼
Hey... What part of me do you like？
Huh？ Hehe... That's a bit embarrassing.
Hmm... I don't quite get it.
Hey... Do you like... when we kiss？
Y-You said that out loud？ Well... I like it, too▼
Hmm... Is that so？ ...Don't tease me.
Well, do you mind people staring at us while we kiss？
From now on, let's do many things together, okay？
Okay, if it's you... Teehee, whatever♪
I don't quite get it... Um.
Do you have a dream for your future？
Okay, I hope your dream comes true. I want to be with you when it happens.
Really... Then you can share my dream, okay？
Your first love... Could it be... me？
Hmm... I'm glad... Then we're both alike. Teehee.
Hmm... Not that I mind, though.
Hey, do you remember the first time we met？
Hm. Me too. I can't possibly forget.
No way. You're teasing me, right？
Do you remember our first date？
Me too. My heart was pounding until my chest hurt. I really remember.
Huh...？ What do you mean by that？
Well... Do you remember when I confessed to you？
Now I love you more than I did back then. Yeah.
Ah... Actually, you feel too embarrassed to say it, right？
Come on, asking about it now is unfair.
You know the answer to that... I love you▼
I love you. I love you so much... I really love you.
Well, I like red and yellow. I like warm colors.
Let me see. I like blue. I like calmer colors.
I enjoy stores where I can go window shopping for clothes.
I like stores that sell cute accessories.
I like cosmetic stores. I'm still learning how to use cosmetics, though.
I like cute clothes. Whose fault was that...？ Hehe...
I like clothes that are neat and feminine. Am I... too plain？
I like simple and casual styles. I have to be active.
We talked a lot today, eh？ Teehee♪
We've talked about so many things today. I'm happy.
We didn't talk much today. See you later, okay？
All right. You need to wake up on time, okay？
Wake up！ It's time！ Come on. Do your best！
Wake up. It's time already.... Hey, wake up. Please.
I'm so sorry！ I forgot when I had to wake you up！
Ah, you woke up▼ Teehee, good morning.
Hey, this will be the last time, okay？ WAKE UP！！
Okay, I'll tell you when it's time. Hehe, you can count on me.
It's time already！ Hehe, is this okay？
Oh no... I missed the time by a little bit！
It's time already. Come on▼ You know what you have to do, right？
Hehe. Do you have an appointment？ Just wondering.
Let's play rock-paper- scissors. If you win best out of 3, I'll give you a reward.
Okay then. Starting with rock... Ready？
Yay, Manaka's victory！ What shall I get as a reward, I wonder♪？
Aaaww... I lost. Okay, as I promised, I'll give you something special.
Ah... Is this okay？ This is special, you know▼？
It's dark outside, right？ So it's nighttime.
It's in the middle of the night. Ah, it's already this late...
Takane Manaka can tell you that it's midnight. That's it.
It's 1 A.M. I'm staying up late.
2 A.M. You can't sleep？ ...Well, me neither.
It's 3 A.M. Hmm, aren't you going to bed yet？
'Morning. It's 6 A.M. Got up so early♪
It's 8 A.M. Do your best for today！
It's 9 o'clock. Hmm？ Are you fully awake？
11 o'clock. You'll probably get hungry soon, right？
It's noon！ What are you going to eat today？ Hehe♪
5It's 1 P.M. Well, do your best in the afternoon, too！
3 P.M. Isn't it time for an afternoon snack？
4 P.M. Just a little bit more. Do your best！
It's now 5 P.M. Finally, it's about time to go home, right？
It's 6 P.M. What are your plans after this？ Hehe.
7 P.M. What are you having for dinner？
8 P.M. Well, prepare and review your lessons, okay？
9 P.M. It's probably time for me to go to bed...
It's 10 P.M. Aren't you going to sleep？
Just 1 more hour and this day will end. You've put in a hard day's work.
